her member for a name of an officer and then explain to the officer what is going on.<br>
<br>
Now in my situation sometimes crap happens and it's tuff to make a judgement off someones opinion on a situation that you don't know.  What I would do in this situation is talk to the person and warn them to be more carefull and decist.  If i discovered they had a bad additude about it and wern't coperative I'd take it further.  <br>
<br>
Now you also have to realize it's a tuff position becase I have to be carefull someone dosn't start complaining about a clan member just becase they hate the person and not becase they did anything wrong. (which dosn't seem to be the case here)<br>
<br>
I'd like to apolagize on behalph of the clan for this instance and if anything like this happens again don't be afraid to get in contact with myself or one of the other officer and we will try to handle it to the best of our abilitie.  We care about our reputation and don't want it to be tarnished.  On the other hand we also care about our members and if something happens that is just a simple misunderstanding we want it resolved before it can get blown out of preportion.<br>
